query:
SELECT
                mirrors_v2.host,
                mirrors_v2.port AS "port: u16",
                mirrors_v2.path AS mirror_path,
                origins.distribution,
                origins.component,
                origins.architecture,
                origins.last_seen
              FROM origins
              JOIN mirrors_v2
              WHERE mirrors_v2.host = ? AND mirrors_v2.port = ? AND mirrors_v2.path = ? AND mirrors_v2.id = origins.mirror_id;
